otesque faces, text, and cartoonlike faces. (This taxonomy is described in a 2000 paper by Santhouse et al.) — location: <a href=\"kindle://book?action=open&#x26;asin=B0082XLY6G&#x26;location=342\" class=\"text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">342</a> ^ref-57663</p>\n<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>",
